  "body": " The middle unit layer is unramified   Assume is tame and put . Then is odd, and tame inertia acts trivially on the middle graded piece Consequently a ramified simple tame module does not occur in that graded piece.    The ramification index of a tame extension of is odd and equals the order of tame inertia. On the odd-depth piece , an inertia element represented by acts through the character . At this character is trivial. A ramified simple module has nontrivial inertia, so its isotypic multiplicity at the middle depth is zero.   "
